title: Ep. 114 - Bootleg Caviar
description:
The boys had a good time with this one as they celebrated Digs being a grownup and talked window washers, Halloween parties, El Chapo, the mafia, the Wright Brothers and more.

Heartland Movie Reviews is at the end of the episode. Today’s review is on Zombieland: Double Tap.
